Marco M. TORRES, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
Honorable Herbert BERKOWITZ, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0511 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 10, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Upon consideration of petitioner's petition and appendix and the circuit court's order affirming the county court's dismissal of the underlying action, the petition for extraordinary writs is denied.

VILLANTI, SLEET, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
